n><span style="font-family:Calibri">other Person concerned, whether relating to the Product or the Loan granted to the Borrower or</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">pursuant to any legal proceedings, at any time before, or after, or during the Loan is in</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">existence, the Borrower undertakes to reimburse the same to the lender along with interest thereon</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">as set forth by the applicable law, or under an arrangement with the dealer, as the case may be</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">immediately on demand and in the manner specified by the lender</span><strong><span style="font-family:Calibri; ">.</span></strong>
