			<span style="font-family:Calibri">The Borrower agrees to pay the Instalment, penalties, fees and other sums due and payable by</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:-2.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">the Borrower to the lender by any of the following modes as approved by the lender considering the</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">information provided by the Borrower:</span>
