			<span style="font-family:Calibri">Unless otherwise decided by the lender at its sole discretion, any amount paid, or prepaid, by the Borrower, either as Instalment or otherwise, shall be adjusted first towards the penalties and</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">charges, if any due and payable by the Borrower, then towards the overdue Instalment(s) and</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:-2.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">then towards balance of the Interest Amount and the Loan principal respectively.</span>
