t-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">first claim on any insurance proceeds shall be that of lender, which proceeds shall be applied by</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:-2.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">lender towards the borrower’s dues in terms hereof or in such other manner as deemed fit by</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">lender.</span>
