				<li style="margin-right:7.05pt; margin-left:28.4pt; padding-left:7.6pt">
					<span style="font-family:Calibri">The borrower</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">agrees, consents</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">and permits</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">lender</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">to disclose</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">to the</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">borrower’s</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">family</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">members (i.e. parents, spouse, children, sisters and brothers) or other persons whose details</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:0.05pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">have been provided by the borrower either in loan application form or otherwise from time to</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:-2.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">time, all necessary or relevant particulars/information relating to the borrower and the loan for</span><span style="font-family:Calibri; letter-spacing:-2.5pt"> </span><span style="font-family:Calibri">any legal purpose required by lender.</span>
				</li>

				<li style="margin-right:7.05pt; margin-left:28.4pt; padding-left:7.6pt">
